@startuml
!theme plain
title Управление расписанием

actor "Диспетчер" as Dispatcher
participant "ScheduleController" as Ctrl
participant "ScheduleService" as Svc
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

== Просмотр расписания группы ==

Dispatcher -> Ctrl: GET /api/schedule?groupId={id}&period=week
Ctrl -> Svc: GetAllAsync(query, ct)
Svc -> DB: SELECT * FROM schedule_entries\nWHERE group_id = @id\nORDER BY day_of_week, start_time
DB --> Svc: List<ScheduleEntry>
Svc -> Svc: Apply period filter (week)
Svc --> Ctrl: Result.Ok({ items, totalCount, page })
Ctrl --> Dispatcher: 200 JSON

== Создание записи ==

Dispatcher -> Ctrl: POST /api/schedule\n{ groupId, teacherId, subject, room, ... }
Ctrl -> Svc: CreateAsync(request, ct)
Svc -> DB: Validate — no overlaps (group, teacher, room)
DB --> Svc: ok
Svc -> DB: INSERT INTO schedule_entries
DB --> Svc: entity
Svc --> Ctrl: Result.Ok(entry)
Ctrl --> Dispatcher: 200 JSON

== Конфликт пересечений ==

Dispatcher -> Ctrl: POST /api/schedule\n{ groupId, teacherId, ... }
Ctrl -> Svc: CreateAsync(request, ct)
Svc -> DB: Validate overlaps
DB --> Svc: Found conflicts
Svc --> Ctrl: Result.Fail("Группа уже занята в это время")
Ctrl --> Dispatcher: 400 Bad Request { error, conflicts }
@enduml
